  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the postoperative outcome of low medium-low rectal endometriosis: Natural orifice
      surgery VS transabdominal surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the postoperative outcome of low medium-low rectal endometriosis: Natural orifice
      surgery VS transabdominal surgery.Both of the two kinds of surgery is conventional,but the
      comparison is still unclear.The investigators divide the patients into two groups, and
      compare the differences of postoperative outcomes by statistics.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
